{"tid":372442,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"賭王四太：澳門氣象局猶疑不決，誰要問責？","createTime":"2017-08-24T10:19:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T13:53:32.000Z","uid":5195,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b58270b3bec690692b9369d373b0f4b9e9376f81","tid":372442,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T10:19:49.000Z","msg":"十級強颱「天鴿」來襲，不單造成本澳難以估計之經濟損失，更不幸造成多條人命傷亡！天災難敵，但人為過失絕不可輕率帶過！鄰近地區早早已向當地居民響起警號，唯獨澳門物理暨氣象局遲遲猶豫不決，竟在最後關頭三小時內才一氣呵成將颱風級數直線由三級調升至十級，導致全澳市民缺乏時間為生命財產做好防預準備，最後演變成全澳市民的一場惡夢；有人損失財物，有人血本無歸，有人遇難身亡，究竟《誰》要負擔這個責任？！<br />\n在此，我們亦要借機感激一群於強颱吹襲下仍堅守崗位，四處奔波，竭力為市民服務的一班前線警務，醫護及消防人員，本人梁安琪向各位致敬！澳門，好在有您！"},{"pid":"e4397f840b0d56c19dbced88e84cf7658f28eaf9","tid":372442,"uid":43721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T10:20:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56896b87f506bf8dfd2d03e61f3b5410c6090317","tid":372442,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T10:21:36.000Z","msg":"澳門女特首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bbf8e748d823788e9b8ab2e4f0da5bd932a4c13","tid":372442,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T10:21:37.000Z","msg":"氣象局班細既"},{"pid":"decd13bdb3433488452239438dee09c86fcc860e","tid":372442,"uid":2054,"like":128,"dislike":2,"score":126,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T10:21:49.000Z","msg":"唔係賭場停電佢會出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e23ddd44599f81cdc0405f147a1b562ac354031a","tid":372442,"uid":5195,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T10:22:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係賭場停電佢會出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hk